Ketika aku masih kecil,

109
00:10:30,891 --> 00:10:33,284
ada seorang wanita.

110
00:10:33,371 --> 00:10:34,938
Dia melempar koin.

111
00:10:36,461 --> 00:10:38,855
Dia menantangku menebaknya,
dan kulakukan.

112
00:10:39,464 --> 00:10:40,552
Kepala.

