Underwood.

144
00:12:33,242 --> 00:12:34,928
Abad ke dua puluh.

145
00:12:35,015 --> 00:12:37,234
Hartford, Connecticut.

146
00:12:37,321 --> 00:12:39,759
Itu di Bumi, sayang.

147
00:12:39,846 --> 00:12:42,239
Sudah melalui enam perang.

148
00:12:42,326 --> 00:12:46,330
Melawan komunisme, fasisme, dan
semua isme di antaranya.

149
