eksperimen

164
00:13:42,169 --> 00:13:43,605
dan tempat interogasi.

165
00:13:43,692 --> 00:13:45,389
Akses khusus ONI.

166
00:13:45,476 --> 00:13:47,478
Jadi, seperti penjara bawah tanah.

167
00:13:51,178 --> 00:13:52,875
Mereka semakin dekat.

168
00:13:52,962 --> 00:13:56,313
Katakan padaku, seperti apa Kessler?

169
00:13:56,836 --> 00:13:58,794
Berapa umurnya?
Dia pasti berumur 9 atau 10?

170
00:13:58,881 --> 00:14:01,101
- Aku yakin dia memujamu.
- Hentikan.

171
00:14:01,188 --> 00:14:02,580
Ketika kau seusia itu,

172
